Title: 'Woman writer in Porto '
DateModified: '2019-02-11'
DatePublished: '2019-02-11'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/woman-writer-in-porto
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Paz Cabo
AuthorCountry: Spain
Text: A woman writer with a broken life travels to Porto to find her novel characters.
  On her way, pays visits to communities, restaurants, best places of the city and
  meet interesting people who takes her to other Portuguese cities, such as Lisbon
  or Faro recreating a new argument for her story. She will write her book and start
  a new life
